				</li>
		
				<li>
					<p>
						<m>H_{3}PO_{4} + {2H}_{2}O \rightarrow HPO_{4}^{2 -} + {2H}_{3}O^{+}</m>
					</p>
				</li>
		
				<li>
					<p>
						<m>H_{3}PO_{4} + {3H}_{2}O \rightarrow PO_{4}^{3 -} + 3H_{3}O^{+}</m>
					</p>
				</li>
		
			</ol></p>
		</li>

		<li>
			<p>
				<em>Consider the acid base reaction shown below:</em>
			</p>
		</li>

	</ol></p>

	<p>
